w countries in a certain region, except country X, revalue their currencies against the US dollar. Then the volume of country X&rsquo;s exports to the countries whose currencies have been revalued will<br />\n<br />\nA.\tincrease.<br />\nB.\tdecrease.<br />\nC.\tremain constant.<br />\nD.\tbe indeterminate.<br />\n<br />\nDSE 16-44 (52%)<br />\nSuppose the countries in a certain region are competitors of exporting goods to the U.S.. The currencies of the countries in the region except that of Country X depreciate against the US dollar. As a result, the volume of Country X&rsquo;s exports to the U.S. will<br />\n<br />\nA.\tdecrease.<br />\nB.\tincrease.<br />\nC.\tremain constant.<br />\nD.\tbe indeterminate."},{"pid":"b68ac2f40bfde3be780778995424bfbd6c915f08","tid":880703,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c170a7fef03e20be3806508c1e43d7850baff059","tid":880703,"uid":35752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T20:29:07.000Z","msg":"咪撚掂AL Econ, 尤其micro, 學壞腦<br />\n唔好花時間去研究除左以前AL之外根本全世界都唔會用既理論<br />\n<br />\n想學好econ可以睇大學教科書"},{"pid":"1e30e175711c63e4f73a375d569da71a4c912c67","tid":880703,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:56:21.000Z","msg":"DSE有啲題型(唔係topic咁簡單)根本係喺AL移植過去，唔好咁片面話AL題目全部唔啱做啦，重點係老師要識揀比學生做。"},{"pid":"90691282196a0459f0bc7b88c4c75db3aec506f5","tid":880703,"uid":35752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e30e175711c63e4f73a375d569da71a4c912c67","tid":880703,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:56:21.000Z","msg":"DSE有啲題型(唔係topic咁簡單)根本係喺AL移植過去，唔好咁片面話AL題目全部唔啱做啦，重點係老師要識揀比學生做。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"唔值得花時間去望AL material"},{"pid":"ec69e404119f634830d0c093af739c26f372a17f","tid":880703,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90691282196a0459f0bc7b88c4c75db3aec506f5","tid":880703,"uid":35752,"like":0,"